OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FUp to four weeks could be cut off the
OL,7,Ftime it takes to complete a house
OL,8,Fpurchase under new plans revealed by
OL,9,Fthe government, which also aims to
OL,10,Freduce the number of unwelcome
OL,11,Fsurprises that can come with buying a
OL,12,Fproperty.
OL,14,FTo help buyers make informed decisions
OL,15,Fearlier on in the process, sellers and
OL,16,Festate agents will have to provide key
OL,17,Finformation upfront in "sales packs"
OL,18,Fat the point of listing.
OL,20,FThis will set out a home's condition,
OL,21,Fleasehold costs and the chain status.
OL,26,@yD@XOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FThe government said this will help to
OL,7,Fcreate a fairer, more transparent
OL,8,Fprocess for everyone involved.
OL,10,FIt is hoped the reforms could also
OL,11,Freduce unexpected and costly
OL,12,Fsurprises, which can lead to sales
OL,13,Fcollapsing, helping people keep more
OL,14,Fmoney in their pockets.
OL,16,FThe changes will also see earlier
OL,17,Fbinding agreements, to stop parties
OL,18,Fwalking away months into negotiations
OL,19,Fwithout a legitimate reason.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FA new code of practice will also raise
OL,7,Fstandards for estate agents, alongside
OL,8,Fproposals for mandatory qualifications
OL,9,Ffor the sector, which could ensure
OL,10,Fagents are properly equipped to
OL,11,Fsupport efficient transactions.
OL,13,FJohan Svanstrom, Rightmove's chief
OL,14,Fexecutive, said their data shows that
OL,15,Ftransactions take an average of 170
OL,16,Fdays to complete and that over one in
OL,17,Ffive transactions initially fall
OL,18,Fthrough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FHe said: "Last year, fall-throughs
OL,7,Falone meant that approximately #900
OL,8,Fmillion in potential stamp duty
OL,9,Freceipts and estate agency commission
OL,10,Fin England was lost, and consumers
OL,11,Flose both precious time, certainty and
OL,12,Fmoney when needing to repeat
OL,13,Ftransaction processes."
OL,15,FThere will also be a shift towards
OL,16,Fdigital systems, rather than paper-
OL,17,Fbased ones.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
