OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FDigital property logbooks and sales
OL,7,Fpacks will help information to be
OL,8,Fshared securely between professionals
OL,9,Fand accessed by buyers and sellers in
OL,10,Freal time, cutting out "back and
OL,11,Fforth" information sharing that can
OL,12,Fhold up sales.
OL,14,FThe government said it will also back
OL,15,Fdigital identity checks, electronic
OL,16,Fsignatures and AI-assisted
OL,17,Fconveyancing to strip out duplication,
OL,18,Freduce fraud risk and accelerate
OL,19,Ftransactions.
OL,26,@rD@XOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said:
OL,7,F"Getting the keys to a home you can
OL,8,Fcall your own is one of the biggest
OL,9,Fevents in anyone's life.
OL,11,F"But right now, the system that should
OL,12,Fprovide support instead turns it into
OL,13,Fa battle, leaving people in limbo and
OL,14,Fputting that opportunity out of reach.
OL,16,F"We're turning the page. Our reforms
OL,17,Fwill bring this outdated process into
OL,18,Fthe modern age, saving people time and
OL,19,Fmoney, and giving them the certainty
OL,20,Fthey deserve."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FFrom next year, plans will include a
OL,7,Fconsultation on estate agent
OL,8,Fqualifications and expanded digital
OL,9,Ftools.
OL,11,FLegislation to require sales packs,
OL,12,Fbinding contracts and digital systems
OL,13,Fis expected by the end of Parliament.
OL,15,FThe phased approach will give the
OL,16,Fsector time to adapt, the government
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FThe government pointed to successes in
OL,7,Fother countries and said the
OL,8,FNetherlands, for example, uses a live
OL,9,Ftracking system for buyers and sellers
OL,10,Fto check their transaction status.
OL,12,FThe plans were welcomed by industry
OL,13,Fexperts, some of whom said first-time
OL,14,Fbuyers in particular will benefit.
OL,16,FHousing is a devolved policy area, and
OL,17,Fthe UK government anticipates that the
OL,18,Fmajority of measures will apply in
OL,19,FEngland, Wales and Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
