CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FAs there is a distinct framework in
OL,7,Fplace in Scotland, the UK government
OL,8,Fdoes not expect its measures to apply
OL,9,Fthere.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAccording to data from Connells Group,
OL,17,Fthis year so far, it is taking around
OL,18,F70 days longer in England and Wales
OL,19,Ftypically to move, from the point of a
OL,20,Fsale being agreed to exchange, than in
OL,21,FScotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
