FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FTV presenter and founder of Move iQ
OL,7,FPhil Spencer said: "I welcome these
OL,8,Fproposals ` they address many of the
OL,9,Fissues consumers have been grappling
OL,10,Fwith for years, from a lack of upfront
OL,11,Finformation to unnecessary delays and
OL,12,Flast-minute surprises."
OL,14,FPaul Whitehead, chief executive of
OL,15,FZoopla, said homeowners "deserve
OL,16,Fbetter than a home-buying process that
OL,17,Ftakes months, falls through too often,
OL,18,Fand leaves everyone poorer for it."
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@WO]wD@YOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
