OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781866076
OL,3,CPlans to simplify house buying to cut
OL,4,Cfour weeks off purchase time
OL,6,FHousing Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,7,F"Buying or selling a home should be
OL,8,Fone of life's great moments and not a
OL,9,Fdrawn-out nightmare of delays, hidden
OL,10,Fcosts and failed deals.
OL,12,F"These changes will make the system
OL,13,Ffaster, fairer and more secure `
OL,14,Fgiving families and first-time buyers
OL,15,Fthe certainty they need all while
OL,16,Fsaving them time and money."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@\O]
